This directory vendors a subset of NVIDIA CUTLASS/CuTe header files
required to build `attn-cuda`.

Source project:
  https://github.com/NVIDIA/cutlass

Original license:
  BSD-3-Clause (see LICENSE.txt in this directory)

Local provenance:
  Imported from CUTLASS include tree via an existing flash-attention dependency.
  The copied headers are redistributed unchanged except for path relocation
  into this repository's third_party tree.
